sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant AI as AI App
    participant C as Cache (LRU)
    participant SM as Supermemory API

    U->>AI: "Help me with my React app"
    AI->>AI: Extract query text:\n"Help me with my React app"
    AI->>C: Cache hit for this query?
    alt Cache HIT
        C->>AI: Return cached memories
        Note over AI: Skip API call!
    else Cache MISS
        AI->>SM: POST /v4/profile\n{ q, containerTag }
        SM->>SM: Semantic search\n(cosine similarity >= 0.6)
        SM->>AI: Returns:\n- static: [facts about user]\n- dynamic: [recent activity]\n- searchResults: [relevant matches]
        AI->>AI: Deduplicate results
        AI->>C: Store in cache (max 100 items)
    end
    AI->>AI: Format as markdown
    AI->>AI: Inject into system prompt
    AI->>U: Response with full context (~50ms)
